title: Age of Empires IV Season Three: Anniversary

media:group.media:title: Age of Empires IV Season Three: Anniversary
media:group.media:description:
We’re excited to celebrate with each and every one of you as part of the first Anniversary of Age of Empires IV and the 25th Anniversary of the Age Franchise! Age of Empires IV Season Three: Anniversary brings with it two new civilizations, the Malians and Ottomans, as well as eight new maps and two new biomes.  

Here are just a few of the other things you can look forward to: 

The start of Ranked Season Three, the introduction of Team Ranked and brand new rewards  

Use Taunts against your opponents and spice up your games with Cheats, including the return of Photon Man 

Naval Balance Rework brings new opportunity to Naval matches 

Waypoint Markers to set unit paths 

Balance changes and bug fixes 

Not only that, but you’ll be able to earn exciting Age-themed rewards during our first set of Seasonal In-Game Events! And there’s still more to come!  

Stay connected with Age of Empires!
